# interrupt.md — Em's interrupt channel

Write anything here and save as memory/interrupt.md
Em will read it at her next natural pause point.

Special commands:
  shutdown    — graceful daemon shutdown

Examples:
  Hey Em, drop what you're doing and reply to this: ...
  shutdown
  New task — pivot to this immediately: ...

The file is consumed (deleted) when Em reads it.
You can also write it programmatically from Perplexity-Em via GitHub.
